games.howToPlayText:
An exciting and addictive pet catching simulator for pokemon lovers. Travel through different roblox worlds and a lot of leveling heroes in one place!

Collect health, upgrade your hero to explore the most amazing worlds of this game. Catch pets in battles, hatch them from cases and eggs, buy and exchange them to get the strongest helpers and friends. Earn money and upgrade your Obby character with the help of ranks and titles.

PC control:
AWSD - running;
Space - jump;
Tab - hide/show the cursor;
Mouse - turn.

On smartphones:
Joystick movement - running;
The up arrow is a jump.

Addictive and addictive lava racing simulator where you can pump up your Obby character for hours, buy cool cars and pass difficult parkours! Lots of cases and boxes and cool cars for tracks will help you have a great time!

Collect stars, charge a slingshot, dynamite or even an entire rocket with energy. Hatch pets from cases and eggs to get more energy. Earn money and pump up your hero with ranks and ranks.

PC controls:
AWSD - run;
Space - jump;
Escape - hide/show cursor;
Mouse - turn.

On smartphones:
Joystick movement - run;
Up arrow - jump.

Block Mine Fuse TNT  this is a story game set in a cubic world, a wonderful world captured by Herobrine. Help Nubik the fuse defeat Herobrine with TNT on a parachute and other arsenal. Pump up and drop TNT on Herobrine.

Free the world from Herobrine and its creepy buildings.
Upgrade and drop TNT, rockets and all your power on cubic settlements.
In the game you will find:
- 31 exciting unique levels;
- - storyline with a cube and a Herobrine;
- various types of TNT;
- Unique Survival mode, create your bases and repel attacks as much as you can;
- Desiccant, Ifrit, Gast, Vardan, Creeper and other bosses;
- New game +, after completing the game (all pumping remains from the last game);
